### Color Tokens

```json
{
  "color": {
    "primary": { "50": "#eff6ff", "100": "#dbeafe", "..": "...", "900": "#1e3a5f" },
    "secondary": { "50": "...", "900": "..." },
    "neutral": { "0": "#ffffff", "50": "...", "950": "#0a0a0a" },
    "semantic": {
      "success": "#16a34a",
      "warning": "#ca8a04",
      "error": "#dc2626",
      "info": "#2563eb"
    },
    "surface": {
      "background": "{color.neutral.0}",
      "foreground": "{color.neutral.950}",
      "muted": "{color.neutral.100}",
      "muted-foreground": "{color.neutral.500}"
    }
  }
}
```

- Generate 10-stop palettes (50–900) for brand colors
- Include semantic colors (success, warning, error, info)
- Include surface tokens referencing palette values
- Validate every foreground/background pair for contrast

